snippet.title: Spectra: Secret Entrances and Spy Bases
snippet.description: Big update in this video- additions include a rain particle effect, ambient rain sound effects, the rough blocking of the entrance to Station 24, a reception area, functioning elevator (with Muzak), and animated screens on each computer.
